	<center>
		<h1>Let's Surprise Amanda!</h1>
		<p>I'm going to put together a little video for Amanda to watch the morning of our wedding. I want to show her how much she is loved by everyone who will be attending our wedding.<br />Upload either an image of you and Amanda together or a selfie video wishing Amanda well. This will only be for her so you don't have to worry about this being shown to a crowd.<br /> Share memories, share fun things you've done, and tell her everything you would want to as if you were in person on the morning of her wedding. <b><em>Have fun with it!</em></b></p><br /><br />
		<%= form_for @thing do |f| %>
			<%= f.label :name, "Your Name" %><br />
			<%= f.text_field :name, placeholder: "Steve Quatrani", class: "form-control" %><br /><br />
			<%= f.label :email, "Your Email" %><br />
			<%= f.text_field :email, placeholder: "spq2461@gmail.com", class: "form-control" %><br />
			
			<%= f.label :image, "Upload An Image" %><br />
			<%= f.file_field :image %><br /><br />
			<%= f.label :video, "Upload a Video" %><br />
			<%= f.file_field :video %><br /><br />
			<%= f.submit "Share Your Love For Amanda", class: "submit-button" %>
		<% end %><br />
	</center>
	<section class="instructions">
		<h2>What to do:</h2>
		<h3>Videos</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>Take a selfie video (<a href="http://www.wikihow.com/Take-Good-Selfies" target="_blank">instructions so you look like a boss</a>)</li>
			<li>Once you are good with it go to allyqwedding.com/surprise either on your phone or computer and upload the video</li>
			<li>Click the choose file button below the "upload a video" label and select the video</li>
			<li>Then click the "Share Your Love For Amanda" button</li>
			<li>Share this with other friends and family!</li>
		</ul>

		<h3>Images</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>Find images of you and Amanda from any time frame.</li>
			<li>Go to allyqwedding.com/surprise either on your phone or computer and upload the image</li>
			<li>If you have multiple you want to upload send them to spq2461@gmail.com</li>
